        "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThis PR adds a comprehensive comparison guide between Shiki, Prism.js, and Highlight.js to help users understand the differences and choose the right library for their needs.\r\n\r\nFixes #599\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n- Added new documentation page at `docs/guide/comparison.md`\r\n- Updated navigation in `docs/.vitepress/config.ts` to include the comparison guide\r\n\r\n## Content Covered\r\n\r\n- Feature comparison table\r\n- Detailed analysis of each library's strengths and considerations\r\n- Performance and bundle size comparisons\r\n- Environment-specific recommendations (SSG, client-side, SSR, edge functions)\r\n- Migration guides from Prism.js and Highlight.js to Shiki\r\n- Decision matrix to help users choose the right library\r\n\r\n## Checklist\r\n\r\n- [x] Content is accurate and unbiased\r\n- [x] Covers all three libraries fairly\r\n- [x] Includes practical migration examples\r\n- [x] Provides clear recommendations for different use cases\r\n- [x] Follows existing documentation style",
