        "body": "## 📊 Feature Overview\nThis PR adds a comprehensive Statistics Dashboard that provides real-time marketplace analytics for the CampusBooks app.\n\n## What's New\n- **StatsScreen Component**: Visual analytics dashboard with overview cards, charts, and insights\n- **Analytics Engine**: `getBookStats()` function for data processing and calculations\n- **UI Integration**: Easy navigation with stats button in main App\n\n## Features\n✅ Overview cards (total listings, available/sold books, avg price)\n✅ Category distribution with visual bar charts\n✅ Listing type breakdown (Sale/Exchange/Donation)\n✅ Price insights (min, average, max)\n✅ Book condition analysis\n\n## Technical Details\n- Added `StatsScreen.js` with responsive design\n- Added `getBookStats()` utility function in `storage.js`\n- Color-coded stat cards with professional UI\n- Handles edge cases (empty data, zero prices)\n\n## Testing\nTested with mock data and various scenarios. App is fully functional.",
